PN,30901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FAs the war in Iran approaches the one-
OL,8,Fmonth mark, a push to resolve the
OL,9,Fconflict appears to have stalled after
OL,10,FIran rejected the 15-point ceasefire
OL,11,Fdeal proposed by the US.
OL,13,FUS officials continue to insist an end
OL,14,Fto hostilities is close, claiming
OL,15,Fregime change has been achieved,
OL,16,Fthough Tehran maintains no such talks
OL,17,Fare underway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThe uncertainty continues to exact a
OL,8,Ftoll on global markets, with oil
OL,9,Fprices beginning to climb back up as
OL,10,Ffears of a drawn-out war grow larger.
OL,12,FIran rejects US ceasefire plan
OL,14,FTwo officials from Pakistan described
OL,15,Fthe 15-point US proposal broadly,
OL,16,Fsaying it included sanctions relief, a
OL,17,Frollback of Iran's nuclear program,
OL,18,Flimits on missiles and reopening the
OL,19,FStrait of Hormuz, through which a
OL,20,Ffifth of the world's oil is normally
OL,21,Fshipped.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FIran issued its own plan via state TV,
OL,8,Fwhich includes a halt to killings of
OL,9,Fits officials, means to make sure no
OL,10,Fother war is waged against it,
OL,11,Freparations for the war, the end of
OL,12,Fhostilities, and Iran's sovereignty
OL,13,Fover the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,15,F"No negotiations have happened with
OL,16,Fthe enemy until now, and we do not
OL,17,Fplan on any negotiations," Iran's
OL,18,Fforeign minister later told state TV.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FTrump insisted at a Republican
OL,8,Ffundraiser on Wednesday night that
OL,9,Ftalks were underway with Iran's
OL,10,Fleaders.
OL,12,F"They are negotiating, by the way, and
OL,13,Fthey want to make a deal so badly, but
OL,14,Fthey're afraid to say it because they
OL,15,Ffigure they'll be killed by their own
OL,16,Fpeople," Trump said.
OL,18,FDespite the hostilities, Trump claimed
OL,19,Fon Wednesday that Iran had gifted the
OL,20,FUS a "very big present worth a
OL,21,Ftremendous amount of money".
OL,26,@tD@AOUxD@HO]|D@FOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FHe continued: "I'm not going to tell
OL,8,Fyou what that present is, but it was a
OL,9,Fvery significant prize.
OL,11,F"They gave it to us, and they said
OL,12,Fthey were going to give it. So that
OL,13,Fmeant one thing to me: We're dealing
OL,14,Fwith the right people.
OL,16,F"It was a very nice thing that was
OL,17,F'oil and gas related' and not related
OL,18,Fto Iran's nuclear program."
OL,20,FOil prices climb
OL,26,@oD@OOUsD@AOUxD@AOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThe rise in oil prices came as Tehran
OL,8,Fon Wednesday dismissed a ceasefire
OL,9,Fplan by the US, after the Trump
OL,10,Fadministration offered a 15-point
OL,11,Fproposal to Iran and the American
OL,12,Fpresident this week delayed a self-
OL,13,Fimposed deadline to "obliterate" its
OL,14,Fpower plants in order to force Iran to
OL,15,Freopen the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,17,FThe Strait of Hormuz, the narrow mouth
OL,18,Fof the Persian Gulf, is considered an
OL,19,Finternational waterway open to all
OL,20,Fshipping.
OL,26,@uD@UOUuD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FAfter Trump's apparent de-escalation
OL,8,Fin hostilities, oil prices had fallen
OL,9,Fto below $100 a barrel, but have since
OL,10,Fseen prices climb back above this mark.
OL,12,F"Weaponising the Strait of Hormuz is
OL,13,Fnot an act of aggression against one
OL,14,Fnation," Sultan al-Jaber, who leads
OL,15,Fthe massive state-run Abu Dhabi
OL,16,FNational Oil Company, said in a speech
OL,17,Ffor an event hosted by the Middle East
OL,18,FInstitute in Washington.
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,F"It is economic terrorism against
OL,8,Fevery consumer, every family that
OL,9,Fdepends on affordable energy and food.
OL,10,FWhen Iran holds Hormuz hostage, every
OL,11,Fnation pays the ransom, at the gas
OL,12,Fpump, at the grocery store and at the
OL,13,Fpharmacy. No country can be allowed to
OL,14,Fdestabilise the global economy in this
OL,15,Fway. Not now. Not ever."
OL,17,FThe comment byal-Jaber signaled the
OL,18,Fhardening rhetoric of the United Arab
OL,19,FEmirates as the war nears its one-
OL,20,Fmonth mark.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
