OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FIran's parliament works to impose fees
OL,8,Fon ships in the Strait of Hormuz
OL,10,FIran's parliament is working on a bill
OL,11,Fto formalise the fees it is reportedly
OL,12,Fcharging on some ships transiting
OL,13,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz, local
OL,14,Fmedia reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,F"This is entirely natural, just as
OL,8,Fgoods pay transit fees when passing
OL,9,Fthrough other corridors, the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz is also a corridor," lawmaker
OL,11,FMohammadreza Rezaei Kouchi reportedly
OL,12,Fsaid. "We provide its security, and it
OL,13,Fis natural that ships and oil tankers
OL,14,Fshould pay such fees."
OL,16,FImposing fees would end that and
OL,17,Flikely be strongly opposed by the Gulf
OL,18,FArab states, the United States and
OL,19,Fothers.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@[O]tD@GOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FOne leading shipping intelligence firm
OL,8,Fsaid on Thursday Iran is running a "de
OL,9,Ffacto 'toll booth' regime" in the
OL,10,FStrait of Hormuz, controlling which
OL,11,Fships come through and getting payment
OL,12,Ffor their safe passage.
OL,14,FLloyd's List Intelligence published an
OL,15,Fanalysis highlighting Iran's practices
OL,16,Fthrough the strait.
OL,18,FIt described vessels having to provide
OL,19,Fmanifests, crew details and their
OL,20,Fdestination to Iran's paramilitary
OL,21,FRevolutionary Guard.
OL,26,@pD@dOUqD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FThe information goes to the Guard's
OL,8,F"Hormozgan Provincial Command for
OL,9,Fsanctions screening, cargo alignment
OL,10,Fchecks that currently prioritizes oil
OL,11,Fover all other commodities, and for
OL,12,Fwhat is described as 'geopolitical
OL,13,Fvetting,'" Lloyd's List said.
OL,15,F"While not all ships are paying a
OL,16,Fdirect toll at least two vessels have
OL,17,Fand the payment is settled in yuan,"
OL,18,FLloyd's List said, referring to
OL,19,FChina's national currency.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@JO]wD@AOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
