OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FTwo killed by missile shrapnel in the
OL,8,FUAE
OL,10,FIn the United Arab Emirates,
OL,11,Fauthorities in Abu Dhabi said two
OL,12,Fpeople had been killed and three
OL,13,Fothers wounded by shrapnel from a
OL,14,Fballistic missile interception.
OL,16,FIn Israel sirens sounded about an hour
OL,17,Fafter sunrise across a large swath of
OL,18,Fcentral Israel, including areas around
OL,19,FTel Aviv and Jerusalem, and in the
OL,20,Foccupied West Bank.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
