OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FIsrael's military said early Thursday
OL,8,Fmorning that Iran had launched
OL,9,Fmissiles toward the country. The first
OL,10,Fsuch alert of the day came after an
OL,11,Funusually long lull of more than 14
OL,12,Fhours.
OL,14,FHezbollah rocket fire, however,
OL,15,Fremained constant overnight in
OL,16,Fnorthern Israel, and once reached the
OL,17,FTel Aviv area overnight.
OL,19,FMissile alerts also sounded on mobile
OL,20,Fphones in Dubai, United Arab Emirates,
OL,21,Fon Thursday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
