CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FSaudi Arabia's Defence Ministry said
OL,8,Fit intercepted multiple drones over
OL,9,Fits oil-rich Eastern Province on
OL,10,FThursday morning.
OL,12,FKuwait reported it was working to
OL,13,Fintercept incoming Iranian fire early
OL,14,FThursday morning. Bahrain sounded its
OL,15,Fmissile alert sirens early Thursday
OL,16,Fmorning.
