OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FHeavy strikes reported around Isfahan
OL,9,FActivists in Iran reported heavy
OL,10,Fstrikes early on Thursday morning
OL,11,Faround Isfahan, a city some 330
OL,12,Fkilometres south of Iran's capital,
OL,13,FTehran.
OL,15,FHam Mihan, an Iranian newspaper
OL,16,Fcritical of the regime, reported
OL,17,Fonline about strikes in the area.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
