OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774602330
OL,3,COil prices rise back to over $100 a
OL,4,Cbarrel as Iran rejects Trump ceasefire
OL,5,Cplan
OL,7,FIsfahan is home to a major Iranian air
OL,8,Fbase and other military sites, as well
OL,9,Fas one of the nuclear sites bombed by
OL,10,Fthe United States during the 12-day
OL,11,Fwar between Israel and Iran in June.
OL,13,FThe semiofficial Fars news agency,
OL,14,Fclose to the paramilitary
OL,15,FRevolutionary Guard, described the
OL,16,Fattacks as targeting "two residential
OL,17,Fareas," without elaborating.
